summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of East Union Street from 25th Avenue to 33rd Avenue et al, in the City of Seattle, by constructing water mains, under Ordinance No. 13195, creating Local Improvement District No. 1195 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
